WEBVTT

33:26.941 --> 33:28.441
Would you like to know
anything else?

33:28.899 --> 33:29.941
Oh! Dad!

33:30.691 --> 33:32.441
Dad, about that thing
I asked you?

33:32.483 --> 33:33.483
-Dad, the keys.
-What?

33:34.399 --> 33:37.483
Remember the course I told you about
at the University of Singapore?

33:37.816 --> 33:40.524
Are there no universities here that
you have to go all the way to Singapore?
